00:13:08.320 --> 00:13:08.910
Senhor,

00:13:09.670 --> 00:13:10.670
Estou aqui

00:13:11.120 --> 00:13:12.270
para

00:13:12.670 --> 00:13:13.870
comunicar consigo

00:13:14.600 --> 00:13:15.840
francamente,

00:13:16.960 --> 00:13:18.480
para que me compreenda melhor

00:13:18.480 --> 00:13:20.360
